channel.title: Project Trifected
channel.description:
[center][u]Intro[/u][/center]
[center]Hello Moparscape. My friend and i are going to be starting a dev team. The base for our server will be Project Insanity/Ri0t. we already have fixed most of the dupes and are working on the bugs. but me and him cant do it all. so we are looking for help. we will be using dropbox so everyone has the files and they will be updated daily.
[u]Fagex-Reborn Positions [/u]
[u]Server Programers[/u] 1. Anthony(me) 2. Auston 3. Open 4. Open
[u]Client Programers[/u] 1. Open 2. Open
Client programmers can choose to use slashes 474 if they want.
[u]Web Designer[/u] 1. evo
[u]Server Features[/u]
1. Perfect combat. 2. Great economy 3. Fully Slayer Tower 4. Npc % Drops Rates are perfect 5. Shops for everything you need 6. Working Skills
[u]Mini-Games[/u] 1. Barrows 100% 2. Duel Arena 100% 3. Fight Caves 90% 4. Jad 0% Redoing 5. Godwars 100%
[u]Items[/u] 1. Barrows brakes when dropped 2. Dfs Making from Kbd 3. Perfect godsword making and dismantling
[/center]
